三個value一定係用conditional statement, 只需要做兩次comparison同一次assignment<img src="/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif" class="hkgmoji" /> <br />
<pre><code data-type="">// default value of int is 0, no need to init
int greatest;
if (x &gt; y) {
    if (x &gt; z) {
        greatest = x;
    } else {
        greatest = z;
    }
} else {
    if (y &gt; z) {
        greatest = y;
    } else {
        greatest = z;
    }
}</code></pre>

